 next to some of the other cases currently before us which Justice BLACKMUN did not select as the vehicle for his announcement that the death penalty is always unconstitutional\u8212\'3ffor example, the case of the 11\u8211\'3fyear\u8211\'3fold girl raped by four men and then killed by stuffing her panties down her throat. See 
