{\f2 \strike0 \ul0 \b0 \sa0 \sb0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
 Court declared that the death penalty must be imposed fairly, and with reasonable consistency, or not at all, see 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1972127195&pubNum=708&originatingDoc=I60e7effe9c5011d9bc61beebb95be672&refType=RP&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.Search)" }{\fldrslt 
