To be fair, a capital sentencing scheme must treat each person convicted of a capital offense with that \u8220\'3fdegree of respect due the uniqueness of the individual.\u8221\'3f 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1978139513&pubNum=708&originatingDoc=I60e7effe9c5011d9bc61beebb95be672&refType=RP&fi=co_pp_sp_708_2964&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.Search)#co_pp_sp_708_2964" }{\fldrslt 
